- 动量: momentum, roc, cmo, adaptive, proc
- 振荡器: rsi_divergence, awesome_oscillator, ultimate_oscillator, tvi, ulcer
- 均线策略: ma_rsi, bb_squeeze, strategy_advanced_kline_echo
- 形态: candlestick, renko_echo, heikin_ashi
- 套利: accumulation_distribution, vpt, cmf, demand_index_echo
- 高级: lstm, elder_ray, aroon, klinger_echo, pivot_points_echo
